---
import Page from '../../layouts/Page.astro'
---
<Page
  title="Voice Rooms"
  label="Product"
  hero="Talk. Don't type."
  sub="Crystal-clear voice and video rooms that make remote communities feel like the same room."
  description="Krenla voice and video rooms — low latency, noise cancellation, screen sharing, and stage mode."
>
  <div class="card-grid">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-ic">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"><path d="M10 3a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v3a4 4 0 0 1-8 0V7a4 4 0 0 1 4-4Z" stroke="rgba(157,130,255,.9)" stroke-width="1.6"/><path d="M5 10a5 5 0 0 0 10 0M10 15v2" stroke="rgba(157,130,255,.9)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Noise cancellation</h3>
      <p>AI-powered noise suppression removes background noise in real time — keyboards, traffic, dogs. People hear you, not your environment.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-ic">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"><rect x="2" y="4" width="16" height="12" rx="2" stroke="rgba(157,130,255,.9)" stroke-width="1.6"/><path d="M7 10h6M10 7v6" stroke="rgba(157,130,255,.9)" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Screen sharing</h3>
      <p>Share your screen, a specific window, or a browser tab with everyone in the room. Works on desktop and mobile.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-ic">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"><path d="M4 6h12M4 10h12M4 14h8" stroke="rgba(157,130,255,.9)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Stage mode</h3>
      <p>Host AMAs, panels, or community events with up to 50 speakers and unlimited listeners. Raise-hand queue built in.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-ic">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"><circle cx="10" cy="10" r="7" stroke="rgba(157,130,255,.9)" stroke-width="1.6"/><path d="M10 6v4l3 2" stroke="rgba(157,130,255,.9)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Low latency</h3>
      <p>Under 100ms end-to-end latency on most connections. Conversations feel natural, not delayed.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="prose">
    <h2>Always-on rooms</h2>
    <p>Voice rooms in Krenla are persistent — they exist as channels in your community sidebar, always ready. Members can drop in and out without needing a link or an invitation, which makes spontaneous conversations happen naturally.</p>

    <h2>Video support</h2>
    <p>Enable cameras individually within any voice room. Video is opt-in — nobody's forced on camera, which keeps rooms accessible for people joining from shared spaces or on the go.</p>

    <h2>Recording</h2>
    <p>Community admins can enable optional recording for voice rooms. Recordings are stored securely, accessible only to members with the appropriate role, and automatically deleted after 30 days unless saved manually.</p>

    <h2>Mobile</h2>
    <p>Voice rooms work fully on iOS and Android. You can keep a room open in the background while using other apps — the connection stays alive and your mic controls stay accessible from the notification tray.</p>
  </div>
</Page>
